			</li>
			<li>
				<h4>Cleaning Crew</h4>
				<p class="txt-wi">Private VRBO Rental, June 2018 — June 2019</p>
				<p>
					Independent cleaning and preparation of 2,500 sq. ft. home
					in preparation of incoming guests. Responsible for all the
					cleaning and set-up of all 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, kitchen,
					dining, living room, and grounds.
				</p>
			</li>
